title: Metal Slug 5 [PC] (Workz) (Really)
description:
Yup...ist's metal slug 5 for PC. Actually you play it w/ an emulator (included!) It,s called M.A.M.E.








Controls... I---UP
            K---DOWN
            J---LEFT
            L---RIGHT

            Q---SHOOT
            W---JUMP
            E--- THROW GRENADES
            R---WAIT AND SEE!!!(on vehicle)
            5---INSERT COIN
            1---PLAYER 1 START
          TAB---MENU


At the start of the game you will see an "insert coin" message. You must press 5 then 1.
If you lost all of your lives and you see the "Continue" message press 5 than 1 than choose a character
